{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494810/extras/Berserker.gif?t=1735988351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REWARDING MELEE COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fluid melee combat is at the heart of this roguelike, where every strike sends limbs flying and blood splattering across the walls. Unleash devastating finishers by chaining slashes, bashes, and kicks into powerful combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494810/extras/MageIce.gif?t=1735988351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENDLESS REPLAYABILITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a surreal hellscape with procedurally generated levels, loot, and quests that ensure no run is ever the same. Unlock unique classes with distinct playstyles, like the spell-slinging Mage, nimble Monk, or greatsword-wielding Berserker!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494810/extras/colorsettings.gif?t=1735988351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SINFUL VISUALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a beautifully rendered, gothic sketch-inspired art style that truly needs to be seen in person to be believed. Plus, enjoy the freedom to fully customize the visuals to your liking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Brutal melee combat that's easy to pick up, but difficult to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful graphic novel visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A varied roster of deadly foes that react to your every move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Hundreds of unique handcrafted rooms within procedurally generated levels  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secret platforming levels in an alternate dimension with rare loot </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Over a dozen playable classes with unique abilities, skills, weapons and items  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A diverse set of weapons including greatswords, spears, claws and magic staves  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Several color palettes to choose from   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Randomly generated quests with powerful rewards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Endless runs for infinite replayability </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> And more still to come! </p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dungeon Novice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/7b9764d7266a2455e3e1568b0cd526bd1868c5e0.jpg"},{"name":"Dungeon Adept","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/436c7641953f4f363be44472e8e1d93c48e3e95f.jpg"},{"name":"Dungeon Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/9b9196e97fffb3c5756ab9639fe955fc54149ff4.jpg"},{"name":"Cave Novice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/dbbce1769265839fb9a9966b622362a52167c94d.jpg"},{"name":"Cave Adept","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/9b81434903107b6b9f3bce55d83fcde4f1e2ed14.jpg"},{"name":"Cave Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/5a5332939fe41390d7fd48318e75c4de9500648f.jpg"},{"name":"Forest Novice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/5b46b1a776b04b1456384fb484b0cef0bf1f0fe7.jpg"},{"name":"Forest Adept","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1494810/9337928625acba51403ff80c00fc726422db936b.jpg"},{"name":"Forest Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images